
---

## 🎯 Goal

This website was created as part of a **Web Development project** to:
- Learn real-world responsive web design
- Implement Bootstrap layout system
- Practice user interface and interaction design for gaming sites

---

## 🧠 Learning Outcomes

- Gained hands-on experience with HTML/CSS layouts
- Improved knowledge of media queries and responsiveness
- Understood how to use icons, fonts, and hover animations for UX enhancement

---

## 📌 Future Improvements

- Add user login and leaderboard
- Integrate with a game API
- Host the site on GitHub Pages or Netlify
- Add game reviews or live chat module

